
 "mondrian"
 A 4k intro for Riverwash 2009 by Alcatraz
 
 Visuals: T$
 Music: p0wl
 Synth: Gopher
 Packer: Crinkler
 
 Requires DirectX9c (including the D3DX library from the June 2006
 SDK update, stored on disk as d3dx9_30.dll, cards.dll) and
 a 3D graphic accelerator and a soundcard.
 Initialization can take a lot of time on slower CPUs.

 Running time: 2:24

 Files included:

 The following versions use 32bit color depth and a 24bit z-buffer:
 * atz_mondrian_640x480.exe
 * atz_mondrian_800x600.bat
 * atz_mondrian_1024x768.bat
 * atz_mondrian_1280x1024.bat

 There is also a windowed version, screen size 640x480.


 Color modes used:
 Display format : X8R8G8B8
 Z-/Stencilbuffer format: D24S8
